msIdentifier.repository: Kislak Center for Special Collections, Rare Books and Manuscripts

msContents.summary: A collection of administrative laws, regulations, and guidelines for the ruler of Rovigo, Italy.
msContents.textLang: Latin, with a few short sections in Italian (p. 169-174)

msItem.title: Collection of laws for the use of the Podestà di Rovigo

supportDesc.extent: 87 leaves : 235 x 168 (116 x 101) mm. bound to 235 x 168 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Contemporary pagination in ink, 2-60, upper outer corners; modern pagination in pencil, 61-175, upper outer corners.
